snippet.title: Toy Story 2 - Buzz Lightyear to the Rescue (1999) - Trailer [PS1]
snippet.description: Trailer for the 1999 PS1 game Toy Story 2 - Buzz Lightyear to the Rescue, ripped from my VHS of Toy Story 2 (1999). Personally one of my favourite games of all time!
